{"word":"προστιμάω","slug":"προστιμάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n90169\" key=\"prostima/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">προστῑμ-άω</orth>, <sense id=\"n90169.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">award further penalty</tr_> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀτίμητος</foreign>), in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Act.\">Act.</a></gram> </gramGrp> of the court, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">π. τοὺς κρίναντας τὴν δίκην ὅ τι χρὴ πρὸς τούτῳ παθεῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:767e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">767e</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:943b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">943b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg003.perseus-grc1:63:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ath.\">Ath.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">63.3</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὸς τῷ ἀργυρίῳ π. δεσμὸν τῷ κλέπτῃ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg024.perseus-grc1:114\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">24.114</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">103</biblScope> </bibl>;